doc.previous: However once the other islands decided to leave meaning that the Netherlands Antilles would become defunct the island council opted to become a special municipality of the Netherlands like Saba and Bonaire
doc.after: Topographically the island is saddle shaped with the 602 meter high dormant volcano Quill from Dutch kuil meaning pit originally referring to its crater to the southeast and the smaller pair Signal Hill Little Mountain or Bergje and Boven Mountain to the northwest The Quill crater is a popular tourist attraction on the island The bulk of the island s population lives in the saddle between the two elevated areas which forms the center of the island
